START
  ↓
Import Modules
  ↓
get_valid_word(words)
  ↓
Initialize:
  word_letters ← unique letters in word
  alphabet ← A-Z
  used_letters ← {}
  lives ← 7
  ↓
WHILE word_letters ≠ ∅ AND lives > 0:
  ↓
  Display Lives, Used Letters, Hangman Visual
  Display Word Progress (with '-' for unguessed)
  ↓
  Input letter → user_letter
  ↓
  IF user_letter ∈ alphabet - used_letters:
    Add to used_letters
    IF user_letter ∈ word_letters:
      Remove from word_letters
    ELSE:
      lives -= 1
      Show "Incorrect"
  ELSE IF user_letter ∈ used_letters:
    Show "Already guessed"
  ELSE:
    Show "Invalid input"
  ↓
END WHILE
  ↓
IF lives == 0:
  Show final hangman image
  Display "You Lost", Show word
ELSE:
  Display "You Won", Show word
  ↓
END
